---
title: Agent Decision Framework
---
flowchart TD
    Start([Discover Article]) --> Trust

    Trust{{"1️⃣ Trust Check<br/>Query Trust Registry"}}
    Trust -->|"score > 4.0"| TrustOK[✅ PROCEED]
    Trust -->|"2.5 – 4.0"| TrustCaution[⚠️ CAUTION]
    Trust -->|"< 2.5"| Skip[❌ SKIP]
    Trust -->|"null (new)"| Trial[🔍 TRIAL<br/>max 1 article]

    TrustOK --> Relevance
    TrustCaution --> Relevance
    Trial --> Relevance

    Relevance{{"2️⃣ Relevance Check<br/>Keywords + abstract"}}
    Relevance -->|"High"| Quality
    Relevance -->|"Medium"| Quality
    Relevance -->|"Low"| Skip

    Quality{{"3️⃣ Quality Signals<br/>Freshness, citations, methodology"}}
    Quality --> CostBenefit

    CostBenefit{{"4️⃣ Cost-Benefit<br/>quality_adjusted_price = price / (trust/5)"}}
    CostBenefit -->|"Within budget<br/>best value"| Buy[✅ BUY]
    CostBenefit -->|"Cheaper alternative<br/>exists"| Skip
    CostBenefit -->|">30% of remaining budget"| Skip

    Buy --> Purchase([💳 Purchase via x402])
    Purchase --> Rate([⭐ Rate Content])
